Everyone in Young Munster RFC is shocked and saddened of the sudden loss of former player Darren Ryan. Our immediate thoughts are with the Ryan family in particular his parents Ray & Trish and siblings Evan ,Gavin and Dawn and his son Raemie who Darren adored.
